headline: Camden: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Houston-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $186.8 million, or $1.70 per share, in the period. The average estimate of eight analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.69 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
